<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #060b15 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .cancel-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.3);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        .cancel-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #facc15;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            color: #facc15;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .urgency-box {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .urgency-box p {
            color: #fca5a5;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #facc15, #fbbf24);
            color: #0f172a;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #facc15;
            color: #facc15;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.1);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .cancel-container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="cancel-container">
        <div class="cancel-icon">😔</div>
        
        <h1>Checkout Cancelado</h1>
        
        <p>
            Entendemos que necesitas más tiempo para decidir. 
            <span class="highlight">No hay problema.</span>
        </p>
        
        <div class="urgency-box">
            <p>⚠️ Recuerda: Solo quedan 38 unidades de 500 disponibles</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>
            Tu Mini-Disc de colección sigue reservado por los próximos 15 minutos.
            Después de eso, estará disponible para otro fan.
        </p>
        
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn">💿 Completar mi Compra</a>
        
        <a href="/ei2" class="btn btn-secondary">🎵 Volver al Álbum</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>